de.thkoeln.bibl.api.lms.slnp.transfer

Class Transfer<T extends Message>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.thkoeln.bibl.api.lms.slnp.transfer.Transfer<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of message the transfer is using
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Request, Response

    public abstract class Transfer<T extends Message>
extends java.lang.Object
    Implements the basic class which describes all SLNP transfer related for handling the messages. A Transfer can be used for receiving and sending messages. All messages are internally stored in a buffer.
    Author:
    Patrick Rogalla
